Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,團長那邊我會向他報告的
